REST (Representable State Transfer)

Create --> POST
Read   --> GET
Update --> PUT
Delete --> DELETE 

Request 
 - Header
 - Param/Body
 - Operations 
 - End Point 

Respone 
 - Header 
 - JSON 

API (Application Programming Interface)
Set of Programming codes that enables data transmission between one software product and another

Web App Browser <----> Internet <----> [API] <----> Web Server -------- Database 

NODE JS - 
Very easy way to build REST API Projects